Common Relic / The Slime Boss / Downfall

messages.content: Pretty pog I get to click the adrenaline unconditionally my command cards proc unconditionally and 5 damage a turn isn't even that bad for a relic anyway
Bot was down for a second I think
Evab's message in bot commands wasn't working

it's a free slime
yay
it's a bit of free damage and eventually becomes 1 point of strength

It's reasonable. Makes it easier to start gaining strength by cycling through slimes, deals 5 damage a turn, which is better than mercury hourglass in single target fights, but worse in aoe fights. Gets better if you have some sources of potency, or any of the cards that care about how many slimes you have like slime brawl and pile on. Not a terribly exciting relic to find, but does a fine job of supporting slime synergies. Sort of similar to young snecko from the suspicious house event, but you don't have to take a curse. I would probably be happy to find this in the early game to help with dealing consistent damage, and would likely buy it from a shop in act 1 or early act 2 if the price is reasonable.
young snecko gets extra value because she is cute

and has synergy with ur cards
